                <h1>Optimize Device Performance: Understanding Background Apps</h1>
                <p>Apps running in the background can significantly impact your device’s performance and battery life. Many applications continue to consume resources even when not actively used, leading to slower speeds and quicker battery drain. Managing background apps is essential for optimizing your device’s functionality and improving overall user experience.</p>
